S"The ultimate video experience is just a tap away with the DIRECTV App for Android tablets. Now you can watch live TV in any room of your home. With select channels, including AUDIENCE Network\xe2\x84\xa2, you can tune in to them whenever and wherever you want \xe2\x80\x93 at home or on the go. Limited programming available. Additional charges may apply.  Available to customers in the USA only. FEATURES- Turn your tablet into a portable TV and watch top TV channels live in any room of your home, plus select channels, including AUDIENCE Network\xe2\x84\xa2, inside or outside your home. - Browse and discover shows, movies and sports. Plus get program descriptions, cast & crew info, and parental ratings \xe2\x80\x93 without interrupting what you are currently watching on TV.- Tap to tune in to any show on your TV from your tablet. - Set your DVR to record your favorite shows from anywhere.- Track your favorite teams and get real-time scores and schedules. HOME SCREEN (Customizable modules)- Customize your home screen by creating a list of your favorite channels. You can add, remove, and reorder as many modules as you like to personalize your DIRECTV experience. Tap on the Customize Layout & Content module to get started.- What\xe2\x80\x99s Hot \xe2\x80\x93 Displays the most popular shows, movies and sports people are watching on DIRECTV right now. - Live TV Streaming \xe2\x80\x93 Lists the live TV channels available to watch on your tablet.- Currently Watching \xe2\x80\x93 More information about the show you are watching now and suggestions for similar shows.- Guide Favorites \xe2\x80\x93 List of favorite channels selected through the Guide.- Channel Guide \xe2\x80\x93 Displays up to 14 days of upcoming shows for a selected channel.- Favorite Channels \xe2\x80\x93 Create a custom list of your favorite channels (by category, his or her list, etc.)- QuickTune \xe2\x80\x93 One-touch selection of your favorite channels by name or icon.- News Channels \xe2\x80\x93 All the news channels in one module.- Kids & Family \xe2\x80\x93 All the kids & family friendly channels in one module.- Sports \xe2\x80\x93 Browse available sports events and scores by game or favorite teams. DEDICATED TABS (Guide, Remote, Playlist, Movies and Sports)- Search the Guide up to 14 days in advance.- View show descriptions, Cast & Crew, Photos, Suggestions & Parental Information.- Share your favorite shows with friends on Facebook and Twitter.- Change channels, set recordings, and get more information.- Organize and delete recorded programs from all of your connected HD DVR receivers.- Set your DVR to record On Demand movies.- View current sports matchups and scores by league, with the option to record or watch on TV.REQUIREMENTS- DIRECTV customers must have a residential home account registered on DIRECTV\xe2\x80\x99s website to access the DIRECTV for Tablets.- Watching select Live TV Streaming channels outside the home requires an active Wi-Fi or mobile network connection. For best performance, connect to a strong Wi-Fi signal.- Available content is based on your current programming package and premium service. Not all content is available to stream at this time.- Live TV Streaming in-home only channels and remote control requires a Wi-Fi connection to your home network and a DIRECTV Plus\xc2\xae HD DVR (models R22, and HR20 or higher) connected to a broadband Internet connection. Remote control also works with HD receivers (models H21, H23 or higher) connected to a broadband Internet connection.- Scheduling a recording requires a Wi-Fi, or mobile network connection and a DIRECTV Plus\xc2\xae DVR or HD DVR. Receivers do not require phone or Internet connection to schedule a recording.- Tips, Tricks, and Customer Support are available on the DIRECTV website.Use of the DIRECTV Tablet Application by DIRECTV customers is subject to DIRECTV's Customer Agreement and Privacy Policy (available on the DIRECTV website)."
